#: ../../boot_options.rst:2
msgid "Boot options"
msgstr "የ ማስነሻ ምርጫ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:4
msgid ""
"Some graphics cards and motherboards don't work well with the open-source "
"drivers present in Linux Mint by default."
msgstr ""
"አንዳንድ የ graphics cards እና motherboards በ ትክክል አይሰሩም በ open-source drivers በ "
"ነባር በ ሊነክስ ሚንት ውስጥ በሚገኘው"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:7
msgid "Compatibility mode"
msgstr "በ ተስማሚ ዘዴ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:9
msgid ""
"The easiest option is to select ``compatibility mode`` from the USB stick "
"(or DVD) boot menu."
msgstr ""
"ቀላሉ መንገድ ይህን መምረጥ ነውt ``በ ተስማሚ ዘዴ`` ከ USB stick (ወይንም ዲቪዲ) ማስነሻ ዝርዝር ውስጥ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:15
msgid "Grub menu (EFI mode)"
msgstr "Grub menu (EFI mode)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:21
msgid "Isolinux menu (BIOS mode)"
msgstr "Isolinux menu (BIOS mode)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:23
msgid "If that doesn't work, you can try the ``nomodeset`` boot option."
msgstr "ይህ ካልሰራ: እርስዎ ይህን ይሞክሩ የ ``nomodeset`` ማስነሻ ምርጫ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:26
msgid "Nomodeset boot option"
msgstr "የ Nomodeset ማስነሻ ምርጫ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:28
msgid ""
"In EFI mode, highlight the ``Start Linux Mint`` option and press :kbd:`e` to "
"modify the boot options."
msgstr ""
"ከ EFI ዘዴ ውስጥ: ያድምቁ የ ``Start Linux Mint`` ምርጫ እና ይጫኑ :kbd:`e` የ ማስነሻ ምርጫ ለ "
"ማሻሻል"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:34
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`F10` to boot."
msgstr "ይቀይሩ ``quiet splash`` በ ``nomodeset`` እና ይጫኑ :kbd:`F10` ለ ማስጀመር"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:36
msgid ""
"In BIOS mode, highlight ``Start Linux Mint`` and press :kbd:`Tab` to modify "
"the boot options."
msgstr ""
"በ BIOS ዘዴ: ያድምቁ ``ሊነክስ ሚንት ማስጀመሪያ`` እና ይጫኑ :kbd:`Tab` የ ማስነሻ ምርጫ ለ ማሻሻል"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:42
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`Enter` to boot."
msgstr "ይቀይሩ ``quiet splash`` በ ``nomodeset`` እና ይጫኑ :kbd:`Enter` ለ ማስነሻ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:45
msgid ""
"Repeat this operation post-install in your grub boot menu and read "
":doc:`drivers` to install additional drivers."
msgstr ""
"ይህን ተግባር ይደጋግሙ ከ ገጠሙ-በኋላ በ እርስዎ grub ማስነሻ ዝርዝር ውስጥ እና ያንብቡ :ሰነድ:`drivers` ለ "
"መግጠም ተጨማሪ drivers."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:48
msgid "Other boot options"
msgstr "ሌሎች የ ማስነሻ ምርጫዎች"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:50
msgid "If you still cannot boot try one of the following solutions:"
msgstr "እርስዎ ማስነሳት ካልቻሉ: ከሚቀጥለው አንዱን ይሞክሩ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:52
msgid "Try ``nouveau.noaccel=1`` instead of ``nomodeset``."
msgstr "ይህን ይሞክሩ ``nouveau.noaccel=1`` ከዚህ ይልቅ ``nomodeset``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:53
msgid ""
"After the installation, use :menuselection:`Advanced Options --> Recovery "
"mode` from the boot menu and choose ``resume``."
msgstr ""
"መግጠም ከ ጨረሱ በኋላ: ይጠቀሙ: ዝርዝር ምርጫ:`የ ረቀቀ ምርጫ --> እንደገና ማግኛ ዘዴ` ከ ማስነሻ ዝርዝር እና "
"ይምረጡ ``ይቀጥሉ``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:56
msgid "Install an older release"
msgstr "አሮጌ እትም መግጠሚያ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:58
msgid ""
"If your computer has compatibility issues with the latest Linux Mint "
"release, install a previous release from the same Linux Mint series."
msgstr ""
"የ እርስዎ ኮምፒዩተር የ መስማማት ችግር ከ ገጠመው ከ ዘመናዊው ሊነክስ ሚንት ጋር: ያለፈውን እትም ይግጠሙ ከ ተመሳሳይ "
"ሊነክስ ሚንት ዝርያ ውስጥ"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:60
msgid ""
"For instance, if you can't install Linux Mint 18.3 (which comes with a 4.10 "
"kernel), install Linux Mint 18 (which comes with a 4.4 kernel) and upgrade "
"to 18.3."
msgstr ""
"ለምሳሌ: እርስዎ መግጠም ካልቻሉ ሊነክስ ሚንት 18.3 (የሚመጣው ከ 4.10 ከረኔል ጋር ነው) ይግጠሙ ሊነክስ ሚንት "
"18 (የሚመጣው ከ 4.4 ከረኔል ጋር ነው) እና ማሻሻያ ወደ 18.3."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:63
msgid ""
"The first release in each series uses an LTS (Long Term Support) kernel. "
"Upgrading from this release to the latest one in the series does not change "
"your kernel."
msgstr ""
"በ መጀመሪያ የሚለቀቀው እትም የሚጠቀመው LTS (ለ ረጅም ጊዜ ድጋፍ) ከረኔል ነው: ይህን እትም ማሻሻል ወደ ዘመናዊው "
"እትም ከረኔሉን አይቀይረውም"

#: ../../boot.rst:2
msgid "Boot Linux Mint"
msgstr "ሊነክስ ሚንት ማስነሻ"

#: ../../boot.rst:4
msgid ""
"Now that you have Linux Mint on a USB stick (or DVD) boot the computer from "
"it."
msgstr "እርስዎ አሁን ሊነክስ ሚንት በ USB stick (ወይንም ዲቪዲ) አለዎት: ኮምፒዩተሩን ያስነሱ"

#: ../../boot.rst:6
msgid "Insert your USB stick (or DVD) into the computer."
msgstr "ያስገቡ የ እርስዎን USB stick (ወይንም ዲቪዲ) ወደ ኮምፒዩተር ውስጥ"

#: ../../boot.rst:8 ../../drivers.rst:23 ../../efi.rst:61 ../../oem.rst:21
msgid "Restart the computer."
msgstr "ኮምፒዩተሩን እንደገና ያስጀምሩ"

#: ../../boot.rst:10
msgid ""
"Before your computer boots your current operating system (Windows, Mac, "
"Linux) you should see your `BIOS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`_ "
"loading screen. Check the screen or your computer's documentation to know "
"which key to press and instruct your computer to boot on USB (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"የ እርስዎ ኮምፒዩተር የ ነበረውን የ መስሪያ ስርአት ከ መጫኑ በፊት (Windows, Mac, Linux) አንዱን ለ "
"እርስዎ መታየት አለበት ይህ `BIOS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`_ loading "
"screen. የ እርስዎን ኮምፒዩተር መመልከቻ ሰነድ ይመርምሩ የትኛውን ቁልፍ ሲጫኑ የ እርስዎን ኮምፒዩተር ማስነሻ "
"እንደሚቀየር ወደ USB (ወይንም ዲቪዲ) ማስጀመሪያ"

#: ../../boot.rst:13
msgid ""
"Most BIOS have a special key you can press to select the boot device and all "
"of them have a special key to enter the BIOS configuration screen (from "
"which you can define the boot order). Depending on the BIOS, these special "
"keys can be :kbd:`Escape`, :kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, :kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, "
":kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12`, or :kbd:`Delete`. That information is usually "
"briefly written on the screen during the boot sequence."
msgstr ""
"በርካታ BIOS የ ተለየ ቁልፍ አላቸው: እርስዎ የሚጫኑት የ ማስነሻ አካል ለ መምረጥ: እና ሁሉም የ ተለየ መግቢያ "
"ቁልፍ አላቸው ወደ BIOS ማሰናጃ መመልከቻ ለ መግባት (እርስዎ የ ማስነሻ ቅደም ተከተል የሚመርጡበት): ይህ ሁኔታ "
"እንደ የ BIOS, አይነት ይለያያል: እነዚህ የ ተለዩ ቁልፎች መሆን ይችላሉ እንደ :kbd:`Escape`, "
":kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, :kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, :kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12` ወይንም "
":kbd:`Delete`. ይህ መረጃ አብዛኛውን ጊዜ ኮምፒዩተሩ በሚነሳበት ጊዜ በ መመልከቻው ላይ ይታያል:"

#: ../../boot.rst:16
msgid ""
"On Macs, keep your finger pressed on the :kbd:`Alt` or :kbd:`Option` key "
"after hearing the boot sound."
msgstr ""
"በ Macs, ተጭነው ይያዙ :kbd:`Alt` ወይንም :kbd:`Option` ቁልፍ የ ማስጀመሪያ ድምፅ ከ ሰሙ በኋላ"

#: ../../boot.rst:18
msgid ""
"The Linux Mint ISO can be booted both in EFI or BIOS mode. In EFI mode it "
"shows a grub menu. In BIOS mode it shows an isolinux menu."
msgstr ""
"የ ሊነክስ ሚንት ISO በ ሁለቱም መንገድ ማስጀመር ይቻላል በ EFI ወይንም BIOS ዘዴ: በ EFI ዘዴ ይህን የ "
"grub ዝርዝር ያሳያል: በ BIOS ዘዴ የ isolinux ዝርዝር ያሳያል."

#: ../../boot.rst:24
msgid "The isolinux menu in BIOS mode"
msgstr "የ isolinux ዝርዝር በ BIOS ዘዴ ውስጥ"

#: ../../boot.rst:30
msgid "The grub menu in EFI mode"
msgstr "የ grub ዝርዝር በ EFI ዘዴ ውስጥ"

#: ../../boot.rst:32
msgid ""
"From one of these menu, press :kbd:`Enter` to start Linux Mint from your USB "
"stick (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"ከ እነዚህ ዝርዝር አንዱን ይጫኑ :kbd:`Enter` ሊነክስ ሚንትን ለ ማስጀመረ ከ እርስዎ USB stick (ወይንም "
"ዲቪዲ) ውስጥ"

#: ../../burn.rst:2
msgid "Create the bootable media"
msgstr "የ ማስነሻ መገናኛ አካል ይፍጠሩ"

#: ../../burn.rst:4
msgid "The easiest way to install Linux Mint is with a USB stick."
msgstr "ቀላሉ መንገድ ሊነክስ ሚንትን ለ መግጠም የ USB stick ይጠቀሙ"

#: ../../burn.rst:6
msgid "If you cannot boot from USB, you can use a blank DVD."
msgstr "እርስዎ ከ USB ማስነሳት ካልቻሉ በ ዲቪዲ ይሞክሩ"

#: ../../burn.rst:9
msgid "How to make a bootable USB stick"
msgstr "እንዴት ነው የ USB stick ማስነሻ የሚፈጥሩት"

#: ../../burn.rst:12
msgid "In Linux Mint"
msgstr "በ ሊነክስ ሚንት ውስጥ"

#: ../../burn.rst:14
msgid ""
"Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Make Bootable USB "
"Stick`, or launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Accessories --> USB Image Writer`."
msgstr ""
"በ ቀኝ-ይጫኑ በ ISO ፋይል ላይ እና ይምረጡ :ዝርዝር መምረጫ:`የ ማስነሻ USB Stick መፍጠሪያ`: ወይንም ያስነሱ "
":ዝርዝር መምረጫ:`ዝርዝር --> ተጨማሪዎች --> USB ምስል መጻፊያ`:"

#: ../../burn.rst:20
msgid "Select your USB device and click :guilabel:`Write`."
msgstr "ይምረጡ የ እርስዎን USB አካል እና ይጫኑ :guilabel:`መጻፊያ`."

#: ../../burn.rst:23
msgid "In Windows, Mac OS, or other Linux distributions"
msgstr "በ Windows, Mac OS, ወይንም ሌሎች የ ሊነክስ ስርጭቶች"

#: ../../burn.rst:25
msgid "Download `Etcher <https://etcher.io/>`_, install it and run it."
msgstr "ያውርዱ `Etcher <https://etcher.io/>`_, ይግጠሙ እና ያስኩዱ"

#: ../../burn.rst:31
msgid "Using Etcher"
msgstr "ይጠቀሙ Etcher"

#: ../../burn.rst:33
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select image` and select your ISO file."
msgstr "ይጫኑ :guilabel:`ምስል ይምረጡ` እና ይምረጡ የ እርስዎን ISO ፋይል"

#: ../../burn.rst:35
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select drive` and select your USB stick."
msgstr "ይጫኑ :guilabel:`ይምረጡ drive` እና ይምረጡ የ እርስዎን USB stick."

#: ../../burn.rst:37
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Flash!`."
msgstr "ይጫኑ :guilabel:`Flash!`."

#: ../../burn.rst:41
msgid "How to make a bootable DVD"
msgstr "የ ዲቪዲ ማስጀመሪያ እንዴት እንደሚፈጥሩ"

#: ../../burn.rst:43
msgid "Optical discs are slow and burning to disc is prone to errors."
msgstr "ኦፕቲካል ዲስክ ዝግተኛ ነው: ወደ ዲስክ ማቃጠል ስህተት ሊያስከትል ይችላል"

#: ../../burn.rst:46
msgid "To prevent issues, burn at the lowest possible speed."
msgstr "ችግር እንዳይፈጠር በ ዝግተኛ ፍጥነት ያቃጥሉ"

#: ../../burn.rst:49
msgid ""
"Burn the content of the ISO onto the DVD, not the ISO file itself. When "
"finished, your DVD should contain directories such as ``boot`` and "
"``casper``, it shouldn't be an empty DVD containing an .iso file."
msgstr ""
"እርስዎ የ ISO ይዞታውን ወደ ዲቪዲ ያቃጥሉ: የ ISO ፋይል አይደለም: በሚጨርሱ ጊዜ: የ እርስዎ ዲቪዲ እነዚህን "
"ዳይሬክቶሪስ መያዝ አለበት እንደ ``boot`` እና ``casper``: ባዶ ዲቪዲ መሆን የለበትም ይህን ያየዘ እንደ "
".iso file."

#: ../../burn.rst:52
msgid "In Linux"
msgstr "በ ሊነክስ ውስጥ"

#: ../../burn.rst:53
msgid "Install and use ``xfburn``."
msgstr "ይግጠሙ እና ይጠቀሙ ``xfburn``."

